Eiffage CEO Says He’s ‘Worried’ About Economic Situation

-- B y   F r a n c o i s   d e   B e a u p u y
-- 
2011-10-18T06:35:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/eiffage-ceo-says-he-s-worried-about-economic-situation.html
Eiffage SA (FGR)  Chief Executive Officer
Pierre Berger said he’s “worried” about the economic
situation, adding that orders are “holding up for now.”  He spoke on BFM radio today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Francois de Beaupuy at 
 fdebeaupuy@bloomberg.net  